behavior load_bowls_and_plates(dishwasher:item):
    body:
        bind bowl: item where:
            is_bowl(bowl) and dirty(bowl)
        bind plate: item where:
            is_plate(plate) and dirty(plate)
        
        achieve inside(bowl, dishwasher)
        achieve inside(plate, dishwasher)
        # Load the dirty bowls and plates into the dishwasher

behavior __goal__():

        bind dishwasher: item where:
            is_dishwasher(dishwasher)
        # Select a dishwasher instance

behavior load_dishwasher(o:item, dishwasher:item):

        achieve inside(o, dishwasher)
        # Load the item into the dishwasher

behavior __goal__():
    body:
        bind dishwasher: item where:
            is_dishwasher(dishwasher)
        # Select a dishwasher
        
        foreach o: item:
            if is_bowl(o) or is_plate(o):
                load_dishwasher(o, dishwasher)
